n│   └── AR-001/                             # Change Request: CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│       ├── proposal.md                     # Proposal document\n│       ├── design.md                       # Detailed design (636 lines)\n│       └── tasks.md                        # Implementation task checklist (ST-4)\n│\n├── cli-toolkit/\n│   ├── design.md                           # CLI (kubectl-agentcube) design\n│   └── spec.md                             # CLI specification\n│\n├── ci-cd/\n│   ├── design.md                           # GitHub Actions workflows design\n│   └── spec.md                             # CI/CD specification\n│\n├── code-execution/\n│   ├── design.md                           # PicoD code execution daemon design\n│   └── spec.md                             # PicoD specification\n│\n├── deployment/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Helm chart, Dockerfiles, Makefile design\n│   ├── spec.md                             # Deployment specification\n│   └── client-go.md                        # Generated client-go library spec\n│\n├── idle-cleanup/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Agentd idle cleanup controller design\n│   └── spec.md                             # Idle cleanup specification\n│\n├── integrations/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Dify plugin + PCAP analyzer example design\n│   └── spec.md                             # Integrations specification\n│\n├── python-sdk/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Python SDK (agentcube-sdk) design\n│   └── spec.md                             # Python SDK specification\n│\n├── sandbox-orchestration/\n│   ├── design.md                           # WorkloadManager + CRD types design (most detailed)\n│   └── spec.md                             # Sandbox orchestration specification\n│\n├── session-routing/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Router/session routing design\n│   └── spec.md                             # Session routing specification\n│\n├── session-store/\n│   ├── design.md                           # Redis/Valkey session store design\n│   └── spec.md                             # Session store specification\n│\n└── testing/\n    └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md           # Core module test contract (TDD Manifest)\n```\n\n### 2. Existing Go Code\n\n**There is NO actual Go source code in this workspace.** The project is entirely in the **design/specification phase**. All Go code exists only as:\n- **Reverse-engineered documentation** from a reference clone at `/tmp/agentcube-ref`\n- **Design specifications** describing what the code should look like\n- **Task checklists** (all unchecked) for implementing the code\n\nThe `.sdd_prompt.md` confirms this is a Stage ST-4 (Implementation) task for AR-001, meaning the code has not yet been written.\n\n### 3. Design Documents and Specs (All Found)\n\n| Directory | Design Doc | Spec Doc | Content Summary |\n|-----------|-----------|----------|-----------------|\n| `changes/AR-001/` | `proposal.md`, `design.md` | `tasks.md` | AgentRuntime CRD type definition for `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | `design.md` (475 lines) | `spec.md` (176 lines) | WorkloadManager, CRD types, K8sClient, Sandbox reconciler, GC, auth |\n| `session-routing/` | `design.md` (160 lines) | `spec.md` (115 lines) | Router, JWT (RS256), reverse proxy, concurrency middleware |\n| `session-store/` | `design.md` (206 lines) | `spec.md` (118 lines) | Redis/Valkey Store interface, ZSET indexing, singleton pattern |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | `design.md` (126 lines) | `spec.md` (69 lines) | Agentd reconciler for Sandbox idle timeout cleanup |\n| `ci-cd/` | `design.md` (190 lines) | `spec.md` (94 lines) | 11 GitHub Actions workflows, E2E test setup, Kind cluster |\n| `code-execution/` | `design.md` (245 lines) | `spec.md` (179 lines) | PicoD daemon: JWT auth, command execution, file APIs |\n| `deployment/` | `design.md` (271 lines) | `spec.md` (96 lines) | Helm chart, Dockerfiles, Makefile targets, RBAC, CRD YAMLs |\n| `deployment/` | `client-go.md` (241 lines) | -- | Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake client generation spec |\n| `python-sdk/` | `design.md` (314 lines) | `spec.md` (133 lines) | CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient, exception hierarchy |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | `design.md` (400 lines) | `spec.md` (197 lines) | kubectl-agentcube CLI: pack, build, publish, invoke, status |\n| `integrations/` | `design.md` (209 lines) | `spec.md` (191 lines) | Dify plugin, PCAP analyzer FastAPI example |\n\n### 4. CRD Definitions and Type Definitions\n\n**No actual CRD YAML or Go type files exist.** However, the design documents specify them in detail:\n\n#### AgentRuntime CRD (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`)\n- **API Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Resource**: `agentruntimes` (Namespaced)\n- **Core types** (from `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` lines 54-101):\n  - `AgentRuntime` struct with `metav1.TypeMeta`, `metav1.ObjectMeta`, `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec`, `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`\n  - `AgentRuntimeSpec` with `Ports []TargetPort`, `Template *SandboxTemplate` (required), `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration` (default 15m), `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration` (default 8h)\n  - `SandboxTemplate` with `Labels`, `Annotations`, `Spec corev1.PodSpec` (required)\n  - `AgentRuntimeStatus` with `Conditions []metav1.Condition`\n  - `AgentRuntimeList` with `Items []AgentRuntime`\n- **Kubebuilder markers**: `+genclient`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"`\n\n#### CodeInterpreter CRD (same API group/version)\n- `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n- `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` (different from SandboxTemplate -- has `Image`, `Command`, `Args`, `Resources`, etc.)\n- Additional fields: `WarmPoolSize *int32`, `AuthMode AuthModeType` (default `picod`, enum `picod|none`)\n\n#### Shared Types\n- `TargetPort`: `PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port uint32`, `Protocol ProtocolType` (default HTTP, enum HTTP|HTTPS)\n- `ProtocolType`: string type with `ProtocolTypeHTTP = \"HTTP\"`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS = \"HTTPS\"`\n- `AuthModeType`: string type with `AuthModePicoD = \"picod\"`, `AuthModeNone = \"none\"`\n\n#### Other Types (from `pkg/common/types`)\n- `SandboxInfo`, `SandboxEntryPoint`, `CreateSandboxRequest`, `CreateSandboxResponse`\n- Kind constants: `AgentRuntimeKind`, `CodeInterpreterKind`, `SandboxKind`, `SandboxClaimsKind`\n\n#### Planned File Layout for `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── doc.go                     # +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package, +groupName\n├── groupversion_info.go       # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n├── register.go                # Kind metadata, SchemeGroupVersion, Resource()\n├── agent_type.go              # AgentRuntime types (core)\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go   # CodeInterpreter + shared types\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go   # Auto-generated by controller-gen\n```\n\n### 5. Build Configuration\n\n**No actual `go.mod`, `Makefile`, or build files exist in the workspace.** However, the design documents specify them extensively:\n\n#### Go Module (from `sandbox-orchestration/design.md`)\n- **Module path**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- **Go version**: `1.24.4` (toolchain `go1.24.9`)\n- **Key dependencies**:\n  - `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`, `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`\n  - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n  - `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox v0.1.1`\n  - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`\n  - `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.17.1`\n  - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.69`\n  - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.2`\n  - `github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1`\n\n#### Makefile Targets (from `deployment/design.md`)\n- **Code generation**: `generate`, `gen-crd`, `gen-client`, `gen-all`, `gen-check`\n- **Build**: `build`, `build-agentd`, `build-router`, `build-all`\n- **Run**: `run`, `run-local`, `run-router`\n- **Docker**: `docker-build`, `docker-build-router`, `docker-build-picod`, `docker-buildx*`, `docker-push*`\n- **Test**: `test`, `e2e`, `e2e-clean`\n- **Tools**: `controller-gen` (v0.17.2), `golangci-lint` (v1.64.1)\n\n#### Code Generation Tools\n- `controller-gen v0.17.2` -- DeepCopy + CRD YAML generation\n- `k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1` -- client-go Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake\n\n### 6. Test Files\n\n**No actual test files exist.** However, comprehensive test specifications are defined:\n\n#### TDD Manifest (`testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md`)\n- **Workload Manager**: Test-WM-1 through Test-WM-4 (Sandbox CRUD, session conflict, pod status sync, cleanup)\n- **Router**: Test-RT-1 through Test-RT-4 (JWT auth, proxy timeout, header passthrough)\n- **Session Store**: Test-ST-1 through Test-ST-2 (serialization, concurrent writes)\n- **PicoD**: Test-PD-1 through Test-PD-2 (OOM, stdout chunking)\n- **Python SDK/CLI**: Test-SDK-1 through Test-SDK-2, Test-CLI-1\n- **Requirements**: T/C ratio > 0.4; every source file must have a corresponding test file\n\n#### Test Spec (`test_spec.md`)\n- TestCase-WM-001/002/003 (Sandbox creation, idempotency, invalid input)\n- TestCase-RT-001/002/003 (Auth intercept, session routing, session expiry)\n- TestCase-ST-001/002 (Redis Set/Get, TTL)\n- TestCase-PD-001/002 (Python execution, syntax error handling)\n- TestCase-SDK-001/002 (Context manager, exception mapping)\n\n#### AR-001 Task Tests (`changes/AR-001/tasks.md`)\n- T-009: Scheme registration test (`TestSchemeRegistration`)\n- T-010: GVK/GVR constants test (`TestGroupVersionConstants`)\n- T-011: Default values test (`TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues`)\n- T-012: DeepCopy test (`TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy`)\n- T-013: ProtocolType enum test (`TestProtocolTypeConstants`)\n\n### 7. AgentRuntime / agentruntime Mentions\n\nFound **270 matches** across the workspace. The most significant references are:\n\n| File | Key Content |\n|------|-------------|\n| `changes/AR-001/design.md` | Complete AgentRuntime CRD design -- struct definitions, kubebuilder markers, API contracts, REST endpoints, example YAML, error handling, test strategy |\n| `changes/AR-001/tasks.md` | 14 task groups (T-001 through T-014) with 60+ subtasks, all unchecked, for implementing `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` |\n| `changes/AR-001/proposal.md` | Change proposal with scope, impact analysis, alternative evaluation, acceptance criteria |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Complete reverse-engineered Go code for `agent_type.go`, `codeinterpreter_types.go`, `groupversion_info.go`, `register.go` |\n| `deployment/client-go.md` | Full client-go generated interface specs for `AgentRuntimeInterface`, `AgentRuntimeInformer`, `AgentRuntimeLister` |\n| `deployment/spec.md` | CRD YAML shipped with Helm chart: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` | Normative requirements for AgentRuntime CRD schema, API registration, field validation |\n\n### Key Finding: Project Status\n\nThis workspace contains **zero implementation code**. It is a comprehensive design/specification artifact for the AgentCube project, reverse-engineered from a reference repository at `/tmp/agentcube-ref`. The `.sdd_prompt.md` file indicates this is a prompt for generating the `design.md` for AR-001 (the AgentRuntime CRD type definition), which is marked as **Stage ST-4 (Implementation)** -- meaning the implementation tasks have been defined but not yet executed. All task checkboxes in `tasks.md` are unchecked.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2899a6fcaffevO8Nan2caMV3sT","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775807860786,"end":1775808017652}}}}
