{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775808022699,"sessionID":"ses_2899a9392ffeaGp6Sez5q41MuG","part":{"id":"prt_d7668033d001b4L1hiNuA2StF7","messageID":"msg_d7667f54e001o6VZh78lcvO2sl","sessionID":"ses_2899a9392ffeaGp6Sez5q41MuG","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_fec93ab8a78a4f4387bc08a7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: `AgentRuntime` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，运行于 Kubernetes API Server 中，API Group 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板，是 WorkloadManager 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 包结构\n10: \n11: ```\n12: pkg/apis/\n13: └── runtime/\n14:     └── v1alpha1/\n15:         ├── doc.go                  # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n16:         ├── groupversion_info.go    # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder (controller-runtime 风格)\n17:         ├── register.go             # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n18:         ├── agent_type.go           # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义（本变更核心）\n19:         ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter CRD + 共享类型 (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n20:         └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go # controller-gen object 自动生成\n21: ```\n22: \n23: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n24: \n25: ```\n26: AgentRuntime 类型定义\n27:   ├── k8s.io/api/core/v1          (corev1.PodSpec 嵌入)\n28:   ├── k8s.io/apimachinery         (metav1.TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Duration, Condition)\n29:   ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (scheme.Builder)\n30:   │\n31:   ├──→ make generate              产出 zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n32:   ├──→ make gen-crd               产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n33:   ├──→ make gen-client            产出 client-go/ (Typed Client, Informer, Lister)\n34:   └──→ WorkloadManager            通过 Informer/Lister 消费 AgentRuntime 资源\n35: ```\n36: \n37: ### 1.4 代码生成工具链\n38: \n39: | 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n40: |------|------|------|\n41: | controller-gen | v0.17.2 | DeepCopy 方法生成 + CRD YAML 生成 |\n42: | k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 | client-go 代码生成 (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake) |\n43: \n44: 生成入口：`make gen-all` → `generate` + `gen-client`。\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ## 2. 数据结构\n49: \n50: ### 2.1 包声明与代码生成标记 (`doc.go`)\n51: \n52: ```go\n53: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n54: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n55: package v1alpha1\n56: ```\n57: \n58: - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package`：触发 controller-gen 为包内所有类型生成 DeepCopy 方法\n59: - `+groupName`：声明 API Group 名称，client-go 代码生成器读取\n60: \n61: ### 2.2 GroupVersion 与 Scheme (`groupversion_info.go`)\n62: \n63: ```go\n64: package v1alpha1\n65: \n66: import (\n67:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n68:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n69: )\n70: \n71: var (\n72:     // GroupVersion 标识 API group 和 version\n73:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n74: \n75:     // SchemeBuilder 用于将类型注册到 scheme\n76:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n77: \n78:     // AddToScheme 将本 group 的所有类型添加到 runtime.Scheme\n79:     AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n80: )\n81: ```\n82: \n83: ### 2.3 Kind 元数据 (`register.go`)\n84: \n85: ```go\n86: package v1alpha1\n87: \n88: import \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n89: \n90: var (\n91:     // CodeInterpreter Kind 元数据\n92:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n93:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n94:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n95:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n96: \n97:     // AgentRuntime Kind 元数据\n98:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n99:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n100:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n101: )\n102: \n103: // SchemeGroupVersion 是 GroupVersion 的别名，兼容 client-go 代码生成器\n104: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n105: \n106: // Resource 返回指定 resource 的 GroupVersionResource\n107: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n108:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n109: }\n110: ```\n111: \n112: ### 2.4 共享类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n113: \n114: 以下类型被 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 共同使用：\n115: \n116: ```go\n117: // ProtocolType 定义端口协议\n118: type ProtocolType string\n119: \n120: const (\n121:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n122:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n123: )\n124: \n125: // TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口\n126: type TargetPort struct {\n127:     // PathPrefix URL 路径前缀（可选）\n128:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n129:     // Name 端口名称（可选）\n130:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n131:     // Port 端口号（必填）\n132:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n133:     // Protocol 协议类型，默认 HTTP\n134:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n135:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n136:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n137: }\n138: \n139: // AuthModeType 定义认证模式\n140: type AuthModeType string\n141: \n142: const (\n143:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n144:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n145: )\n146: ```\n147: \n148: ### 2.5 AgentRuntime 核心类型 (`agent_type.go`)\n149: \n150: #### 2.5.1 AgentRuntime (CR 根类型)\n151: \n152: ```go\n153: // +genclient\n154: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n155: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n156: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n157: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes\n158: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n159: \n160: // AgentRuntime 声明式定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板。\n161: type AgentRuntime struct {\n162:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n163:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n164: \n165:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n166:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n167: }\n168: ```\n169: \n170: **Kubebuilder 标记说明：**\n171: \n172: | 标记 | 作用 |\n173: |------|------|\n174: | `+genclient` | 为 client-go 代码生成器标识此类型需要生成 Typed Client |\n175: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | DeepCopy 方法实现 runtime.Object 接口 |\n176: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | 标记为 kubebuilder object root，生成 DeepCopyObject |\n177: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | 启用 `/status` 子资源，分离 spec/status 更新权限 |\n178: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes` | 命名空间级资源，REST 路径复数形式为 `agentruntimes` |\n179: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"...` | `kubectl get agentruntimes` 输出中显示 Age 列 |\n180: \n181: #### 2.5.2 AgentRuntimeSpec\n182: \n183: ```go\n184: // AgentRuntimeSpec 定义 AgentRuntime 的期望状态。\n185: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n186:     // TargetPort 沙箱暴露的端口列表\n187:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n188: \n189:     // PodTemplate 沙箱 Pod 模板（必填）\n190:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n191:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n192: \n193:     // SessionTimeout 会话空闲超时时间，默认 15m\n194:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n195:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n196: \n197:     // MaxSessionDuration 会话最大存活时间，默认 8h\n198:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n199:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n200: }\n201: ```\n202: \n203: **字段语义：**\n204: \n205: | 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n206: |------|------|------|--------|------|\n207: | `targetPort` | `[]TargetPort` | 否 | `[]` | 沙箱暴露的端口配置，为空时 WorkloadManager 不配置路由端口 |\n208: | `podTemplate` | `*SandboxTemplate` | 是 | — | 沙箱 Pod 模板，嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec` |\n209: | `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `15m` | 空闲超时后沙箱被清理 |\n210: | `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `8h` | 沙箱从创建到强制销毁的最大时长 |\n211: \n212: #### 2.5.3 SandboxTemplate\n213: \n214: ```go\n215: // SandboxTemplate 定义沙箱 Pod 的模板。\n216: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n217:     // Labels 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外标签\n218:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n219: \n220:     // Annotations 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外注解\n221:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n222: \n223:     // Spec Pod 规格（必填），直接使用 Kubernetes 原生 PodSpec\n224:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n225:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\"`\n226: }\n227: ```\n228: \n229: **设计决策：** `SandboxTemplate` 直接嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec` 而非自定义字段子集。\n230: \n231: | 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n232: |------|------|------|\n233: | 嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`（已选） | 完整 Kubernetes 能力；无需维护字段映射；与 agent-sandbox 项目一致 | CRD YAML 较大（~1000 行） |\n234: | 自定义字段子集 | CRD YAML 精简 | 丢失 Kubernetes 原生能力；需持续同步 PodSpec 变更 |\n235: \n236: #### 2.5.4 AgentRuntimeStatus\n237: \n238: ```go\n239: // AgentRuntimeStatus 定义 AgentRuntime 的观测状态。\n240: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n241:     // Conditions 资源状态条件列表\n242:     // +optional\n243:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n244: }\n245: ```\n246: \n247: **预期 Condition 类型（由 WorkloadManager 控制器写入）：**\n248: \n249: | Type | Status | Reason | 说明 |\n250: |------|--------|--------|------|\n251: | `Ready` | `True` | `SandboxRunning` | 沙箱已成功创建并运行 |\n252: | `Ready` | `False` | `SandboxFailed` | 沙箱创建失败或异常终止 |\n253: | `Ready` | `Unknown` | `Pending` | 沙箱正在创建中 |\n254: \n255: #### 2.5.5 AgentRuntimeList\n256: \n257: ```go\n258: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n259: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n260: \n261: // AgentRuntimeList 包含 AgentRuntime 资源列表。\n262: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n263:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n264:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n265:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n266: }\n267: ```\n268: \n269: ### 2.6 数据结构关系图\n270: \n271: ```\n272: AgentRuntime\n273: ├── TypeMeta (apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, kind: AgentRuntime)\n274: ├── ObjectMeta (name, namespace, labels, annotations, uid, creationTimestamp, ...)\n275: ├── Spec: AgentRuntimeSpec\n276: │   ├── targetPort: []TargetPort\n277: │   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n278: │   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n279: │   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n280: │   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (default: HTTP, enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n281: │   ├── podTemplate: *SandboxTemplate (required)\n282: │   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n283: │   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n284: │   │   └── spec: corev1.PodSpec (required)\n285: │   │       ├── containers: []corev1.Container\n286: │   │       ├── volumes: []corev1.Volume\n287: │   │       ├── serviceAccountName: string\n288: │   │       ├── nodeSelector: map[string]string\n289: │   │       ├── tolerations: []corev1.Toleration\n290: │   │       └── ... (完整 Kubernetes PodSpec)\n291: │   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (default: \"15m\")\n292: │   └── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (default: \"8h\")\n293: └── Status: AgentRuntimeStatus\n294:     └── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n295:         └── {type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime, observedGeneration}\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ---\n299: \n300: ## 3. API 契约\n301: \n302: ### 3.1 GroupVersionKind (GVK)\n303: \n304: | 组件 | 值 |\n305: |------|-----|\n306: | API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n307: | Version | `v1alpha1` |\n308: | Kind | `AgentRuntime` |\n309: | ListKind | `AgentRuntimeList` |\n310: \n311: ### 3.2 GroupVersionResource (GVR)\n312: \n313: | 组件 | 值 |\n314: |------|-----|\n315: | Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n316: | Version | `v1alpha1` |\n317: | Resource | `agentruntimes` |\n318: | Scope | Namespaced |\n319: \n320: ### 3.3 REST API 端点\n321: \n322: Kubernetes API Server 自动暴露以下端点：\n323: \n324: | Method | Path | 说明 |\n325: |--------|------|------|\n326: | `POST` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes` | 创建 AgentRuntime |\n327: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 获取单个 AgentRuntime |\n328: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes` | 列出命名空间下的 AgentRuntime |\n329: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes` | 列出所有命名空间的 AgentRuntime |\n330: | `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 更新 AgentRuntime (spec) |\n331: | `PATCH` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 补丁更新 |\n332: | `DELETE` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n333: | `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}/status` | 更新 status 子资源 |\n334: \n335: ### 3.4 示例 YAML\n336: \n337: ```yaml\n338: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n339: kind: AgentRuntime\n340: metadata:\n341:   name: python-sandbox\n342:   namespace: default\n343: spec:\n344:   targetPort:\n345:     - name: web\n346:       port: 8080\n347:       protocol: HTTP\n348:       pathPrefix: /\n349:   podTemplate:\n350:     labels:\n351:       app: python-agent\n352:     annotations:\n353:       agentcube.io/runtime: python-3.11\n354:     spec:\n355:       containers:\n356:         - name: sandbox\n357:           image: python:3.11-slim\n358:           ports:\n359:             - containerPort: 8080\n360:           resources:\n361:             requests:\n362:               cpu: \"100m\"\n363:               memory: \"128Mi\"\n364:             limits:\n365:               cpu: \"1\"\n366:               memory: \"512Mi\"\n367:   sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n368:   maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n369: ```\n370: \n371: ### 3.5 Scheme 注册\n372: \n373: AgentRuntime 类型通过 `SchemeBuilder` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`：\n374: \n375: ```go\n376: func init() {\n377:     SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})\n378: }\n379: ```\n380: \n381: 下游组件（WorkloadManager、client-go fake client）通过调用 `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 将类型注册到自身 scheme。\n382: \n383: ### 3.6 生成的 client-go 接口\n384: \n385: `make gen-client` 基于本类型定义生成以下接口（详见 `deployment/client-go.md`）：\n386: \n387: | 接口 | 方法 | 说明 |\n388: |------|------|------|\n389: | `AgentRuntimeInterface` | `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` | Typed REST 客户端 |\n390: | `AgentRuntimeInformer` | `Informer()`, `Lister()` | 共享 Informer + Lister |\n391: | `AgentRuntimeLister` | `List(selector)`, `AgentRuntimes(namespace)` | 只读缓存索引 |\n392: | `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` | `List(selector)`, `Get(name)` | 命名空间级只读索引 |\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ## 4. 错误处理\n397: \n398: ### 4.1 验证错误\n399: \n400: Kubernetes API Server 在资源创建/更新时自动执行 kubebuilder 标记定义的验证：\n401: \n402: | 场景 | 验证标记 | 预期错误 |\n403: |------|----------|----------|\n404: | `podTemplate` 缺失 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.podTemplate: Required value` |\n405: | `podTemplate.spec` 缺失 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.podTemplate.spec: Required value` |\n406: | `protocol` 非法值 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.targetPort[*].protocol: Unsupported value` |\n407: | `sessionTimeout` 格式错误 | 隐式 (metav1.Duration 解析) | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: 解析失败 |\n408: \n409: ### 4.2 应用层错误\n410: \n411: `pkg/api/errors.go` 定义与 AgentRuntime 相关的错误类型：\n412: \n413: ```go\n414: var (\n415:     ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound = errors.New(\"agent runtime not found\")\n416:     ErrTemplateMissing      = errors.New(\"resource has no pod template\")\n417: )\n418: \n419: func NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind string) error\n420: ```\n421: \n422: | 错误 | 触发场景 | HTTP 状态码 |\n423: |------|----------|-------------|\n424: | `ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound` | WorkloadManager 查找不存在的 AgentRuntime | 404 |\n425: | `ErrTemplateMissing` | AgentRuntime 的 `podTemplate` 为 nil | 400 |\n426: | `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError` | 按 namespace/name 查找 SandboxTemplate 失败 | 404 |\n427: \n428: ### 4.3 默认值处理\n429: \n430: | 字段 | 默认值 | 应用时机 |\n431: |------|--------|----------|\n432: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` | Kubernetes API Server 在 CREATE 时通过 defaulting webhook 或 controller-gen 生成的 CRD default 注入 |\n433: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` | 同上 |\n434: | `targetPort[*].protocol` | `HTTP` | 同上 |\n435: | `targetPort` | `[]` (空切片) | Go 零值，无需注入 |\n436: \n437: ### 4.4 并发安全\n438: \n439: 本包定义的类型本身无状态，不涉及并发。类型实例的并发安全由使用者（Informer cache、WorkloadManager）保证：\n440: \n441: - Informer 缓存通过 `cache.SharedIndexInformer` 的 RWMutex 保证读写安全\n442: - DeepCopy 方法确保跨 goroutine 传递时进行值拷贝\n443: \n444: ---\n445: \n446: ## 5. 测试策略\n447: \n448: ### 5.1 单元测试\n449: \n450: #### 5.1.1 Scheme 注册测试\n451: \n452: ```go\n453: func TestSchemeRegistration(t *testing.T) {\n454:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n455:     err := v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n456:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n457: \n458:     // 验证 GVK 可识别\n459:     gvk := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n460:     obj, err := scheme.New(gvk)\n461:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n462:     assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}, obj)\n463: \n464:     // 验证 List 类型\n465:     gvkList := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntimeList\")\n466:     objList, err := scheme.New(gvkList)\n467:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n468:     assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList{}, objList)\n469: }\n470: ```\n471: \n472: #### 5.1.2 GVK/GVR 常量测试\n473: \n474: ```go\n475: func TestGroupVersionConstants(t *testing.T) {\n476:     assert.Equal(t, \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", v1alpha1.GroupVersion.Group)\n477:     assert.Equal(t, \"v1alpha1\", v1alpha1.GroupVersion.Version)\n478:     assert.Equal(t, \"AgentRuntime\", v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeKind)\n479:     assert.Equal(t, \"AgentRuntimeList\", v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeListKind)\n480: \n481:     gvr := v1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntimes\")\n482:     assert.Equal(t, schema.GroupVersionResource{\n483:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n484:     }, gvr)\n485: }\n486: ```\n487: \n488: #### 5.1.3 默认值测试\n489: \n490: ```go\n491: func TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues(t *testing.T) {\n492:     ar := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n493:         Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n494:             Template: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n495:                 Spec: corev1.PodSpec{\n496:                     Containers: []corev1.Container{{Name: \"test\", Image: \"test:latest\"}},\n497:                 },\n498:             },\n499:         },\n500:     }\n501: \n502:     // 验证 Go 零值行为\n503:     assert.Nil(t, ar.Spec.SessionTimeout)\n504:     assert.Nil(t, ar.Spec.MaxSessionDuration)\n505:     assert.Empty(t, ar.Spec.Ports)\n506: \n507:     // 验证默认值由 CRD default 注入（模拟 API Server 行为）\n508:     // 注意：实际默认值由 Kubernetes API Server 在 CREATE 时注入\n509:     // 此处仅验证类型可接受 nil 值\n510: }\n511: ```\n512: \n513: #### 5.1.4 DeepCopy 生成测试\n514: \n515: ```go\n516: func TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n517:     original := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n518:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n519:         Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n520:             Ports: []v1alpha1.TargetPort{{Name: \"web\", Port: 8080, Protocol: v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTP}},\n521:             Template: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n522:                 Labels: map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n523:                 Spec: corev1.PodSpec{\n524:                     Containers: []corev1.Container{{Name: \"c\", Image: \"test:latest\"}},\n525:                 },\n526:             },\n527:             SessionTimeout:   &metav1.Duration{Duration: 30 * time.Minute},\n528:             MaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 4 * time.Hour},\n529:         },\n530:         Status: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeStatus{\n531:             Conditions: []metav1.Condition{{\n532:                 Type:   \"Ready\",\n533:                 Status: metav1.ConditionTrue,\n534:                 Reason: \"SandboxRunning\",\n535:             }},\n536:         },\n537:     }\n538: \n539:     copy := original.DeepCopy()\n540: \n541:     // 验证值相等\n542:     assert.Equal(t, original.Name, copy.Name)\n543:     assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.Ports[0].Port, copy.Spec.Ports[0].Port)\n544: \n545:     // 验证引用独立（修改副本不影响原件）\n546:     copy.Spec.Ports[0].Port = 9090\n547:     assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), original.Spec.Ports[0].Port)\n548: \n549:     copy.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"] = \"modified\"\n550:     assert.Equal(t, \"test\", original.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"])\n551: }\n552: ```\n553: \n554: #### 5.1.5 ProtocolType 枚举测试\n555: \n556: ```go\n557: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n558:     assert.Equal(t, v1alpha1.ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n559:     assert.Equal(t, v1alpha1.ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n560: }\n561: ```\n562: \n563: ### 5.2 测试文件布局\n564: \n565: ```\n566: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n567: ├── agent_type.go\n568: ├── agent_type_test.go        # AgentRuntime 类型测试\n569: ├── codeinterpreter_types.go\n570: ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go # 共享类型测试\n571: ├── groupversion_info.go\n572: ├── groupversion_info_test.go # Scheme 注册测试\n573: ├── register.go\n574: ├── register_test.go          # GVK/GVR 常量测试\n575: └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n576: ```\n577: \n578: ### 5.3 测试运行\n579: \n580: ```bash\n581: # 运行 pkg/apis 下所有测试\n582: go test ./pkg/apis/... -v\n583: \n584: # 运行带覆盖率\n585: go test ./pkg/apis/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\n586: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n587: ```\n588: \n589: ### 5.4 TDD 关联\n590: \n591: 本变更与 TDD 规范的关联用例：\n592: \n593: | TDD 用例 | 关联 | 说明 |\n594: |----------|------|------|\n595: | TestCase-WM-001 | 间接 | AgentRuntime 类型是 Sandbox 创建接口的输入基础 |\n596: | TestCase-WM-003 | 间接 | 缺失 `podTemplate` 的拦截依赖 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记 |\n597: \n598: ---\n599: \n600: ## 6. 实现步骤\n601: \n602: ### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n603: \n604: 1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` — 包声明 + 生成标记\n605: 2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` — GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n606: 3. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` — Kind 元数据\n607: 4. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` — 共享类型 (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n608: 5. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` — AgentRuntime 核心类型\n609: 6. 运行 `make generate` — 生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n610: \n611: ### 6.2 验证检查清单\n612: \n613: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n614: - [ ] `make generate` 成功生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n615: - [ ] `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n616: - [ ] `AgentRuntime` GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n617: - [ ] GVR resource = `agentruntimes`\n618: - [ ] `SessionTimeout` 默认值标记 = `15m`\n619: - [ ] `MaxSessionDuration` 默认值标记 = `8h`\n620: - [ ] `SandboxTemplate.Spec` 类型为 `corev1.PodSpec` 且标记为 Required\n621: - [ ] `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` 已添加\n622: - [ ] `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` Age 列已添加\n623: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n624: \n625: ---\n626: \n627: ## 7. 后续变更\n628: \n629: 本变更完成后，以下变更可并行开展：\n630: \n631: | 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n632: |------|----------|------|\n633: | AR-002 | 依赖 AR-001 | CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义（共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`） |\n634: | CRD YAML 生成 | 依赖 AR-001 | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记产出 CRD YAML |\n635: | client-go 生成 | 依赖 AR-001 | `make gen-client` 产出 Typed Client/Informer/Lister |\n636: | WorkloadManager | 依赖 client-go 生成 | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 AgentRuntime 资源 |\n\n(End of file - total 636 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`AgentRuntime` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，运行于 Kubernetes API Server 中，API Group 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板，是 WorkloadManager 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                  # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n        ├── groupversion_info.go    # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder (controller-runtime 风格)\n        ├── register.go             # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n        ├── agent_type.go           # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义（本变更核心）\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter CRD + 共享类型 (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go # controller-gen object 自动生成","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775808022688,"end":1775808022696}}}}
