"`；`GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T-004: 创建 register.go — Kind 元数据与 Resource 辅助函数\n43: \n44: - [ ] T-004.01 定义 `AgentRuntimeKind = \"AgentRuntime\"`\n45: - [ ] T-004.02 定义 `AgentRuntimeListKind = \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n46: - [ ] T-004.03 定义 `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")`\n47: - [ ] T-004.04 定义 `SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion`（别名，兼容 client-go 代码生成）\n48: - [ ] T-004.05 定义 `func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource` 返回 `GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)`\n49: - [ ] T-004.06 定义 CodeInterpreter Kind 元数据（`CodeInterpreterKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupKind`、`CodeInterpreterListKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`）供后续 AR-002 使用\n50: \n51: **验收**: `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回 `{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\"}`\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## T-005: 创建 codeinterpreter_types.go — 共享类型定义\n56: \n57: - [ ] T-005.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n58: - [ ] T-005.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n59: - [ ] T-005.03 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`（带 `+kubebuilder:default=HTTP` 和 `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` 标记）\n60: - [ ] T-005.04 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n61: - [ ] T-005.05 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n62: - [ ] T-005.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n63: \n64: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`TargetPort` 结构体字段与 JSON tag 映射正确\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## T-006: 创建 agent_type.go — AgentRuntime 核心类型定义\n69: \n70: ### T-006.1: AgentRuntime 根类型\n71: \n72: - [ ] T-006.1.01 定义 `type AgentRuntime struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n73: - [ ] T-006.1.02 字段 `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`）\n74: - [ ] T-006.1.03 字段 `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`（JSON tag: `status,omitempty`）\n75: - [ ] T-006.1.04 添加标记 `+genclient`\n76: - [ ] T-006.1.05 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n77: - [ ] T-006.1.06 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n78: - [ ] T-006.1.07 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n79: - [ ] T-006.1.08 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`\n80: - [ ] T-006.1.09 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n81: \n82: ### T-006.2: AgentRuntimeSpec\n83: \n84: - [ ] T-006.2.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeSpec struct`\n85: - [ ] T-006.2.02 字段 `Ports []TargetPort`（JSON tag: `targetPort,omitempty`）\n86: - [ ] T-006.2.03 字段 `Template *SandboxTemplate`（JSON tag: `podTemplate`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n87: - [ ] T-006.2.04 字段 `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `sessionTimeout,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` 标记）\n88: - [ ] T-006.2.05 字段 `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `maxSessionDuration,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` 标记）\n89: \n90: ### T-006.3: SandboxTemplate\n91: \n92: - [ ] T-006.3.01 定义 `type SandboxTemplate struct`\n93: - [ ] T-006.3.02 字段 `Labels map[string]string`（JSON tag: `labels,omitempty`）\n94: - [ ] T-006.3.03 字段 `Annotations map[string]string`（JSON tag: `annotations,omitempty`）\n95: - [ ] T-006.3.04 字段 `Spec corev1.PodSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n96: - [ ] T-006.3.05 导入 `corev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"`\n97: \n98: ### T-006.4: AgentRuntimeStatus\n99: \n100: - [ ] T-006.4.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeStatus struct`\n101: - [ ] T-006.4.02 字段 `Conditions []metav1.Condition`（JSON tag: `conditions,omitempty`，带 `+optional` 标记）\n102: \n103: ### T-006.5: AgentRuntimeList\n104: \n105: - [ ] T-006.5.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeList struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ListMeta`\n106: - [ ] T-006.5.02 字段 `Items []AgentRuntime`（JSON tag: `items`）\n107: - [ ] T-006.5.03 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n108: - [ ] T-006.5.04 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n109: \n110: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；所有 kubebuilder 标记存在；GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## T-007: 创建 Scheme 注册 init() 函数\n115: \n116: - [ ] T-007.01 在 `agent_type.go` 或独立文件中添加 `func init()` 调用 `SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})`\n117: \n118: **验收**: `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 成功将 `AgentRuntime` 和 `AgentRuntimeList` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## T-008: 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n123: \n124: - [ ] T-008.01 运行 `make generate`（或 `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\" output:dir=./pkg/apis`）\n125: - [ ] T-008.02 验证 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 已生成在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 下\n126: - [ ] T-008.03 验证生成的 DeepCopy 方法覆盖 `AgentRuntime`、`AgentRuntimeSpec`、`AgentRuntimeStatus`、`AgentRuntimeList`、`SandboxTemplate`、`TargetPort`\n127: \n128: **验收**: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 存在；`go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n129: \n130: ---\n131: \n132: ## T-009: 编写单元测试 — Scheme 注册测试\n133: \n134: - [ ] T-009.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go`\n135: - [ ] T-009.02 测试 `AddToScheme(scheme)` 无错误\n136: - [ ] T-009.03 测试 `scheme.New(GVK)` 可识别 `AgentRuntime` 类型\n137: - [ ] T-009.04 测试 `scheme.New(GVKList)` 可识别 `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n138: \n139: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestSchemeRegistration -v` 通过\n140: \n141: ---\n142: \n143: ## T-010: 编写单元测试 — GVK/GVR 常量测试\n144: \n145: - [ ] T-010.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register_test.go`\n146: - [ ] T-010.02 测试 `GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`\n147: - [ ] T-010.03 测试 `GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n148: - [ ] T-010.04 测试 `AgentRuntimeKind == \"AgentRuntime\"`\n149: - [ ] T-010.05 测试 `AgentRuntimeListKind == \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n150: - [ ] T-010.06 测试 `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回正